General.Name: Ata Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi AS
General.Description: Ata Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. operates in REIT sector in Turkey. The company focuses on commercial real estate valuables and projects. Its projects include real estate, retail, office, and logistics. Ata Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. was founded in 1997 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.
